data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_4badac0bd53c85bd0069a7e6afa2e48190a1ace7c46dd4db01","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":248,"text":"**Smart Eyewear (Contoso Galaxy Innovations – SmartView Glasses)** is a wearable glasses platform that blends everyday eyewear with augmented reality, hands-free controls, and capture capabilities .\n\n### Key features\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface**: Overlays digital content and interactive elements in your field of view for an “AR glasses” experience .\n- **Voice-controlled AI agent**: Built-in voice control lets you operate the glasses and interact with an AI assistant without using your hands .\n- **HD video recording with 3D audio**: Records high-definition video along with spatial (3D) audio for more immersive playback .\n- **UV protection + blue light filtering**: Lens protection designed to help reduce UV exposure and filter blue light .\n- **Wireless charging + extended battery life**: Supports wireless charging and is designed to last longer between charges .\n\n### What the documentation highlights beyond features\nThe guide also covers **sizing/fit adjustments**, **care and maintenance**, an **AR break-in period** (getting used to the experience), **safety tips**, and **troubleshooting** ."}

